## Overview

Code Groups organize multiple code examples into a tabbed interface, making it easy to show the same concept across different programming languages or provide alternative implementations. Each tab contains a CodeSnippet component with full syntax highlighting, line numbering, and interactive features.

<Callout type="tip">
Use Code Groups when documenting API endpoints, SDK usage, or any feature that has multiple language implementations.
</Callout>

