### Copy to Clipboard

The copy button in the top-right corner copies the currently active tab's code content. Individual CodeSnippet copy buttons are automatically hidden inside Code Groups to avoid duplication.

### AI Integration

Click the "Ask AI" button to open an AI chat with the code from the active tab pre-filled with the prompt: "Explain this code to me."

<Callout type="info">
The AI assistant uses keyboard shortcuts: Cmd+I (macOS) or Ctrl+I (Windows/Linux) to toggle the sidebar.
</Callout>

### Syntax Highlighting

All code snippets use Shiki syntax highlighting with dual theme support (light and dark modes). Themes are pre-rendered to eliminate visual flash when switching between modes.

