## Technical Implementation

Code Groups are implemented in two variants:

- **MDX Documentation** (`src/components/mdx/code-group.tsx`) - Standard documentation pages with smaller text styling
- **API Documentation** (`src/components/tags/code-group.tsx`) - Right-side code snippets with larger text styling

Both variants share core functionality:

- Automatic tab label extraction from child CodeSnippet components
- Active tab state management
- Copy-to-clipboard for the active tab's content
- AI integration for code explanation
- Child prop manipulation to ensure seamless visual integration

<Callout type="info">
The component automatically clones children and overrides props to remove borders, disable inline copy buttons, and suppress title display for a cohesive tabbed interface.
</Callout>

